WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:46.009
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.140 --> 01:48.920
[Episode 32]

02:12.730 --> 02:13.270
Hello, Mr. Wen.

02:13.310 --> 02:14.080
Hello, Mr. Wen.

02:19.820 --> 02:20.670
It's him, yeah?

02:26.140 --> 02:28.680
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

02:30.650 --> 02:32.220
Your blood sugar's a bit high.

02:34.600 --> 02:35.400
Is it?

02:35.710 --> 02:36.790
Blood sugar?

02:38.910 --> 02:42.760
[Glycated albumin]
[Glucose]

02:43.870 --> 02:45.040
It really is.

02:46.000 --> 02:47.920
Why didn't you find out last time?

02:49.280 --> 02:50.620
You know it, right?

02:53.120 --> 02:54.870
I... I know.

02:55.510 --> 02:58.200
I've been taking metformin for six months.

03:00.830 --> 03:01.950
Keep taking it then.

03:09.140 --> 03:19.270
[Pharmacy]

03:11.920 --> 03:13.430
You've been taking medicine for over six months,

03:13.450 --> 03:14.280
yet you didn't tell me.

03:14.350 --> 03:15.230
Why'd you lie about your

03:15.230 --> 03:15.990
check-up results?

03:19.310 --> 03:21.280
It's not a big deal.

03:21.570 --> 03:23.280
Your grandma has diabetes.

03:23.910 --> 03:25.630
I have this gene.

03:25.650 --> 03:27.030
It's just a matter of time.

03:27.150 --> 03:29.060
How can you say that?

03:29.110 --> 03:30.030
If you be careful,

03:30.050 --> 03:31.240
it can be prevented.

03:31.610 --> 03:32.740
Careful how?

03:32.920 --> 03:34.900
I'd have to watch what I eat.

03:34.930 --> 03:36.800
I'd be so miserable.

03:37.150 --> 03:37.670
Besides,

03:37.690 --> 03:38.770
I'm not scared of diabetes.

03:38.960 --> 03:40.670
I'll just take insulin jabs.

03:40.690 --> 03:41.760
Can't you be healthy

03:41.800 --> 03:42.470
instead?

03:42.520 --> 03:43.660
Must you get jabs?

03:44.840 --> 03:46.530
If I've to stick to a strict diet

03:46.650 --> 03:48.820
to live a long, healthy life,

03:49.120 --> 03:50.790
I'd rather

03:50.810 --> 03:52.030
eat what I like

03:52.070 --> 03:53.329
and eat good food,

03:53.360 --> 03:55.160
even if it means I'll die earlier.

03:55.230 --> 03:56.110
Hey, watch it.

03:56.140 --> 03:57.690
How could you say that?

04:00.690 --> 04:01.840
Seriously.

04:01.920 --> 04:04.060
Don't you want to see me get married?

04:04.740 --> 04:06.320
Don't you want to hug your grandchild?

04:06.390 --> 04:08.010
Of course, I want to.

04:08.960 --> 04:10.610
Hurry up then.

04:11.390 --> 04:13.530
Has Jiang told his parents about our meeting?

04:15.300 --> 04:16.190
Listen.

04:16.350 --> 04:18.029
I have an operation in a few days.

04:18.060 --> 04:19.220
I can't face them

04:19.269 --> 04:20.480
lying in the hospital bed.

04:20.630 --> 04:22.690
You're quite thorough, huh?

04:22.720 --> 04:23.590
I've told him.

04:23.710 --> 04:24.950
But he's busy with a case,

04:24.970 --> 04:26.640
and I have work here too.

04:27.410 --> 04:27.980
Sure.

04:28.640 --> 04:30.480
You two go ahead with work.

04:30.550 --> 04:32.630
I'll prepare the gifts.

04:34.670 --> 04:35.630
Just let me know

04:35.670 --> 04:36.830
when you're free.

04:38.510 --> 04:39.470
What first gifts should I get

04:39.470 --> 04:40.310
for my in-laws?

04:41.710 --> 04:42.760
I-Is the mall

04:42.800 --> 04:44.030
near your home big?

04:44.600 --> 04:46.780
It's quite big.

04:46.830 --> 04:48.110
But don't go alone.

04:48.130 --> 04:49.130
You might get lost.

04:49.190 --> 04:50.290
I'll go with you after work.

04:50.740 --> 04:51.900
Are you kidding?

04:51.990 --> 04:53.190
Who am I?

04:53.240 --> 04:55.300
I travel around the world.

04:56.070 --> 04:57.450
Can I get lost?

04:57.750 --> 04:58.230
Don't worry.

04:58.310 --> 04:58.740
Just

04:58.790 --> 05:00.160
focus on your work.

05:00.190 --> 05:01.310
I'll go by myself.

05:02.030 --> 05:03.670
Just take good care of yourself.

05:03.710 --> 05:04.230
It's fine.

05:05.550 --> 05:07.190
How about a scarf for his mom?

05:07.440 --> 05:08.570
Does his dad smoke?

05:09.270 --> 05:09.950
This won't do.

05:09.990 --> 05:11.630
I have to buy some clothes to dress up

05:11.680 --> 05:12.270
for the meeting.

05:12.270 --> 05:13.410
Just shop for yourself.

05:13.480 --> 05:14.500
Yes, for myself.

05:14.590 --> 05:15.190
Yuan Li.

05:15.190 --> 05:16.620
Please go to window no. 8 to get the medicine.

05:16.770 --> 05:17.910
I'll get it for you.

05:18.070 --> 05:18.470
Okay.

05:21.480 --> 05:23.610
[Hang up]

05:21.480 --> 05:23.610
[Mr. Wen]

05:25.910 --> 05:26.730
Mr. Wen.

05:27.270 --> 05:28.340
Did you hear it?

06:05.070 --> 06:05.680
Yue.

06:05.700 --> 06:06.220
He's out.

06:06.240 --> 06:06.920
I see him.

06:14.470 --> 06:15.810
Let's see where he's going.

06:22.360 --> 06:22.990
This one's good too.

06:22.990 --> 06:23.710
Take a look.

06:23.730 --> 06:24.510
Let me see.

06:24.720 --> 06:25.350
Let me see.

06:26.710 --> 06:28.290
Let me see other colors.

06:28.380 --> 06:29.990
I think the long one's nice.

06:31.330 --> 06:32.720
Don't push, can you?

06:32.750 --> 06:33.320
I'm sorry.

06:33.350 --> 06:34.000
I didn't mean it.

06:34.070 --> 06:35.090
You didn't?

06:36.390 --> 06:37.200
Who knows if you

06:37.230 --> 06:38.110
stole my stuff?

06:38.390 --> 06:39.280
Hey!

06:39.310 --> 06:40.330
Watch your words!

06:40.390 --> 06:41.430
Why'd I steal from you?

06:41.470 --> 06:42.550
Why are you yelling?

06:42.590 --> 06:43.440
Feeling guilty?

06:43.510 --> 06:44.240
Feel guilty

06:44.300 --> 06:45.110
for what?

06:45.140 --> 06:46.190
Can you be reasonable?

06:46.210 --> 06:46.990
Who are you pointing at?

06:47.010 --> 06:47.680
At you! What—

06:47.700 --> 06:48.190
Excuse me.

06:48.220 --> 06:49.020
I saw it.

06:49.040 --> 06:50.150
She didn't steal from you.

06:50.240 --> 06:50.970
See?

06:51.100 --> 06:52.080
And who are you?

06:52.100 --> 06:53.270
Why'd I trust you?

06:53.730 --> 06:55.200
Are you in cahoots?

06:55.390 --> 06:56.260
Look over there.

06:58.159 --> 06:58.860
Left.

07:00.030 --> 07:01.000
Another one here.

07:01.340 --> 07:02.690
Filled with surveillance cameras.

07:02.990 --> 07:04.030
If you're worried,

07:04.070 --> 07:04.820
you can take a look.

07:04.950 --> 07:05.870
Yes, go and check.

07:05.950 --> 07:06.840
Forget it.

07:06.920 --> 07:07.560
I'm busy!

07:07.580 --> 07:08.840
What surveillance footage?

07:08.870 --> 07:09.590
Are you crazy?

07:09.710 --> 07:10.390
Let's go.

07:10.470 --> 07:11.270
Don't go!

07:11.350 --> 07:12.750
Weren't you making a point? Go on!

07:14.030 --> 07:15.060
I can't believe her.

07:16.430 --> 07:17.680
Thank you, young man.

07:17.830 --> 07:18.510
You're welcome.

07:19.150 --> 07:19.550
Ma'am.

07:20.710 --> 07:21.790
Do you remember me?

07:23.550 --> 07:25.860
Y-You are...

07:26.310 --> 07:28.300
I’m Lu Yan’s senior.

07:28.780 --> 07:29.920
When she was in university,

07:29.950 --> 07:30.910
she was sick,

07:30.950 --> 07:32.030
and I even visited her.

07:36.510 --> 07:37.230
You're the

07:37.270 --> 07:38.750
student union member,

07:38.840 --> 07:39.470
right?

07:39.610 --> 07:40.120
Yes.

07:40.590 --> 07:41.150
Wow!

07:41.230 --> 07:42.390
What a coincidence,

07:42.430 --> 07:42.909
huh?

07:43.070 --> 07:43.590
Yes, yes.

07:43.610 --> 07:45.310
I was shopping around.

07:45.620 --> 07:47.010
You bought so many things?

07:47.200 --> 07:48.000
Yes.

07:49.110 --> 07:49.909
If you're free,

07:49.930 --> 07:50.990
I can shop with you.

07:51.270 --> 07:52.330
No, no need.

07:52.390 --> 07:53.190
I-I...

07:53.210 --> 07:54.110
I'm about done.

07:54.140 --> 07:54.960
I should go home.

07:56.510 --> 07:57.390
I have a car.

07:57.390 --> 07:58.150
I'll give you a ride.

07:59.960 --> 08:01.230
How could I trouble you?

08:01.230 --> 08:01.790
It's okay.

08:01.790 --> 08:02.670
I'll go back by myself.

08:02.670 --> 08:03.470
It's okay. Let me help you.

08:03.470 --> 08:04.610
Let me help you.

08:04.820 --> 08:05.570
It's okay.

08:06.520 --> 08:07.220
Alright.

08:07.310 --> 08:08.150
Thank you then.

08:08.190 --> 08:08.880
You're welcome.

08:08.990 --> 08:09.810
What's your name?

08:09.870 --> 08:10.480
Wen Peng.

08:10.800 --> 08:11.470
Wen Peng!

08:12.690 --> 08:13.830
I remember now.

08:13.870 --> 08:15.030
Thank you for taking care

08:15.050 --> 08:16.440
of Yan in the hospital.

08:16.510 --> 08:16.930
Right?

08:17.030 --> 08:17.670
It's my duty.

08:17.730 --> 08:19.080
She was

08:19.150 --> 08:20.280
hospitalized

08:20.310 --> 08:21.890
because her best friend

08:22.080 --> 08:23.630
Deng Man passed away, right?

08:24.210 --> 08:24.710
Yes.

08:24.830 --> 08:25.750
My memory.

08:28.730 --> 08:29.940
Be careful.

08:32.679 --> 08:33.630
This way.

08:37.190 --> 08:37.870
Yue.

08:38.120 --> 08:39.470
Who's that woman with him?

08:41.110 --> 08:41.799
I don't know.

08:41.890 --> 08:43.220
Let's follow them first.

09:07.360 --> 09:07.860
Hello?

09:07.930 --> 09:08.510
Captain Jiang.

09:08.540 --> 09:10.430
We found Wen Peng

09:10.450 --> 09:12.090
with a middle-aged woman.

09:12.110 --> 09:13.250
But we don't know who she is.

09:13.270 --> 09:14.270
Anything else?

09:14.350 --> 09:14.960
No.

09:16.450 --> 09:16.890
Okay.

09:16.910 --> 09:17.750
Keep an eye on him.

09:17.950 --> 09:19.880
Call me if anything happens.

09:20.150 --> 09:20.550
Okay.

09:21.600 --> 09:22.030
Okay.

09:31.770 --> 09:32.510
You're here

09:32.550 --> 09:33.790
for an operation, right?

09:35.580 --> 09:37.950
I also want to use this time

09:37.970 --> 09:39.270
to meet the parents

09:39.270 --> 09:40.550
of Yan's boyfriend.

09:41.850 --> 09:42.990
Is she and Jiang Chengyi

09:43.030 --> 09:44.230
getting married?

09:45.630 --> 09:46.080
Yes.

09:46.110 --> 09:47.310
You know Jiang Chengyi too?

09:47.350 --> 09:48.350
Were you classmates?

09:48.370 --> 09:48.770
Yes.

09:48.790 --> 09:50.370
Gosh, my memory.

09:50.530 --> 09:51.690
The two of them

09:51.750 --> 09:52.940
aren't anxious,

09:53.190 --> 09:54.700
but I heard from

09:54.780 --> 09:55.860
Yan that

09:55.880 --> 09:57.810
Jiang Chengyi’s mom is very anxious.

09:59.820 --> 10:01.250
So I thought

10:01.420 --> 10:03.250
that since I'm here now,

10:03.320 --> 10:04.550
we should just settle

10:04.630 --> 10:05.760
their marriage.

10:06.190 --> 10:07.910
They'll get married sooner or later anyway.

10:07.940 --> 10:09.070
After they get married,

10:09.150 --> 10:10.670
they can do their own thing,

10:10.690 --> 10:11.330
don't you think?

10:12.630 --> 10:13.440
Sounds good.

10:14.290 --> 10:14.950
Mrs. Jiang.

10:14.950 --> 10:16.650
If it's convenient,

10:16.820 --> 10:18.190
I can introduce you a few

10:18.230 --> 10:19.140
wedding agencies.

10:20.640 --> 10:21.750
That's great.

10:22.700 --> 10:23.340
Thank you.

10:23.440 --> 10:24.210
You're welcome.

10:30.140 --> 10:31.030
It's Yan.

10:33.480 --> 10:34.460
Hello, Mom.

10:35.210 --> 10:37.030
We've agreed on dinner tonight.

10:37.150 --> 10:38.310
I have an operation.

10:38.330 --> 10:39.910
It'll be over around seven.

10:39.950 --> 10:41.310
Jiang Chengyi will pick you up at home

10:41.350 --> 10:42.490
and then pick me up at the hospital.

10:42.760 --> 10:43.370
How about this?

10:43.870 --> 10:44.310
I...

10:44.470 --> 10:45.070
Well...

10:45.120 --> 10:45.760
I-I've to...

10:45.790 --> 10:46.870
get my hair done first.

10:47.910 --> 10:48.640
Okay.

10:49.050 --> 10:50.040
And then, um,

10:50.080 --> 10:51.200
I’ll call Jiang.

10:51.230 --> 10:52.100
I have his number too.

10:52.190 --> 10:53.440
I'll call him myself.

10:54.140 --> 10:55.310
Okay, okay.

10:57.440 --> 10:58.040
Look.

10:58.510 --> 11:00.020
We're meeting tonight.

11:00.050 --> 11:00.490
Look.

11:00.590 --> 11:01.910
Thanks to my foresight,

11:01.930 --> 11:02.450
I have

11:02.510 --> 11:03.470
the gifts too.

11:03.510 --> 11:04.850
Yes, it's quite a lot.

11:08.490 --> 11:09.790
Um, Wen Peng,

11:09.840 --> 11:10.990
ask the driver

11:11.030 --> 11:12.230
to drop me off

11:12.350 --> 11:13.230
after turning left.

11:13.250 --> 11:14.200
There's a salon there.

11:14.270 --> 11:15.170
I'll go wash my hair.

11:15.430 --> 11:16.630
Sure, no problem.

11:19.210 --> 11:20.150
Lucky I met you,

11:20.230 --> 11:20.850
you know?

11:20.910 --> 11:21.630
Otherwise,

11:21.650 --> 11:22.770
I'd still be arguing

11:22.840 --> 11:24.200
with that woman in the mall.

11:51.350 --> 11:52.370
Careful, Mrs. Jiang.

11:54.840 --> 11:56.030
Thank you, Wen Peng.

11:56.120 --> 11:56.630
You're welcome.

11:56.710 --> 11:57.430
Here, your stuff.

11:57.460 --> 11:58.130
Okay.

11:59.000 --> 12:00.100
Come visit when you have time.

12:00.130 --> 12:00.470
Okay.

12:00.490 --> 12:01.120
Take care.

12:01.790 --> 12:02.400
Bye.

12:11.850 --> 12:13.180
Yue, Wen Peng turned left.

12:38.500 --> 12:39.280
Jiang.

12:39.880 --> 12:41.000
I'm done.

12:41.630 --> 12:42.530
You're here?

12:46.400 --> 12:47.430
I'm near the exit.

12:47.300 --> 12:50.460
[No reversing on this one-way street]

12:48.540 --> 12:49.070
Here, Auntie.

12:49.090 --> 12:49.780
See me?

12:49.910 --> 12:50.590
I see you!

12:50.590 --> 12:51.510
I'm here!

12:52.070 --> 12:52.930
Wait for me.

13:21.990 --> 13:23.350
Hello, is this the ambulance?

13:23.440 --> 13:24.550
There's a car accident here.

13:24.990 --> 13:25.750
Yes, yes!

13:26.250 --> 13:27.560
Hello, emergency?

13:27.750 --> 13:29.270
There was a car accident in Yangpu Road.

13:29.320 --> 13:29.960
Someone's injured.

13:44.320 --> 13:45.830
[Operating Room] [ICU]

13:52.480 --> 13:53.860
Lu, leave it to us.

13:54.040 --> 13:54.800
Don't worry.

14:09.030 --> 14:09.720
Yes.

14:10.300 --> 14:11.620
Yes, Director Xing. I know.

14:12.570 --> 14:14.030
We're trying to use

14:14.080 --> 14:14.630
the Skynet system

14:14.670 --> 14:15.960
to locate the hit-and-run driver

14:16.030 --> 14:17.390
and see where he's been

14:17.410 --> 14:18.620
and who he had contact with.

14:19.780 --> 14:21.180
Yes, please approve it.

14:22.310 --> 14:22.970
Yes!

14:23.350 --> 14:24.180
Thank you, Director Xing.

14:24.270 --> 14:24.950
Bye.

14:27.360 --> 14:28.720
Contact Sihan immediately.

14:28.750 --> 14:29.670
Ask him to come sub us

14:29.690 --> 14:30.260
with Li Yong.

14:30.310 --> 14:31.270
Let's go back to the station.

14:31.310 --> 14:31.900
Got it.

14:35.110 --> 14:35.590
Mr. Wen.

14:37.540 --> 14:38.730
The money's in the car.

14:39.270 --> 14:41.430
Take it with you when you leave.

14:42.360 --> 14:43.040
Remember.

14:43.360 --> 14:44.430
Don't do anything

14:44.510 --> 14:45.690
when you leave.

14:46.470 --> 14:48.690
If the police question you,

14:48.760 --> 14:49.910
blame it all

14:49.950 --> 14:50.750
on me.

14:51.230 --> 14:51.830
Wen.

14:52.220 --> 14:53.080
I'm not leaving.

14:55.100 --> 14:55.810
Why?

14:57.050 --> 14:58.100
All these years,

14:58.440 --> 14:59.740
you've been taking care of my family.

15:00.350 --> 15:01.710
You gave me everything.

15:02.730 --> 15:03.590
I can risk it all

15:03.630 --> 15:04.510
for you.

15:08.150 --> 15:08.710
Alright then.

15:09.670 --> 15:10.940
Do one more thing for me.

15:11.190 --> 15:11.870
Go ahead.

15:14.790 --> 15:16.060
I need a car.

15:16.090 --> 15:17.340
A used car's fine.

15:17.670 --> 15:18.350
No problem.

15:18.950 --> 15:20.150
I'll go get it done,

15:20.270 --> 15:21.590
and I'll text you the address.

15:38.330 --> 15:41.090
[Outpatient]

15:41.180 --> 15:45.310
[ICU]

15:46.850 --> 15:48.450
[Smart healthcare is the future]

15:52.250 --> 15:55.110
[Operating Room]

16:05.510 --> 16:14.590
[ICU]

18:51.380 --> 18:52.430
[Operating Room]

18:55.470 --> 18:56.230
How is it?

18:56.830 --> 18:58.230
The intracranial bleeding has stopped.

18:58.870 --> 19:00.070
But the hematoma caused

19:00.070 --> 19:01.940
by the prior trauma was too serious.

19:02.310 --> 19:03.030
In the next few days,

19:03.040 --> 19:04.490
brain swelling is inevitable.

19:05.030 --> 19:06.100
Her recovery

19:06.510 --> 19:07.310
will depend on

19:07.310 --> 19:08.310
the next 48 hours.

19:09.280 --> 19:10.350
She's been transferred

19:10.390 --> 19:11.510
to the ICU ward.

19:12.230 --> 19:12.670
I'll go

19:12.670 --> 19:13.580
see her now.

19:13.880 --> 19:14.390
Okay.

19:14.910 --> 19:19.580
[Medical Personnel Passageway]

19:16.430 --> 19:17.020
Doctor.

19:17.490 --> 19:19.050
How long will it usually

19:19.720 --> 19:21.280
take for her to wake up?

19:22.580 --> 19:23.410
It's hard to say.

19:24.270 --> 19:25.510
It depends on the patient's

19:25.510 --> 19:26.150
willpower.

19:27.390 --> 19:28.030
But

19:28.060 --> 19:30.090
with this much bleeding,

19:30.560 --> 19:31.860
even if she woke up,

19:32.310 --> 19:33.150
it's very likely that

19:33.190 --> 19:34.220
she'd be in a vegetative state.

20:12.200 --> 20:14.580
Do you want to... take a break?

20:15.080 --> 20:16.630
I'll keep watch here.

20:17.460 --> 20:18.110
I'm fine.

20:25.960 --> 20:26.780
The doctor said...

20:29.090 --> 20:30.550
she will make it through.

20:32.280 --> 20:33.770
She definitely will.

20:48.490 --> 20:49.450
I'm sorry.

20:53.790 --> 20:54.910
I failed to protect your mom...

21:00.110 --> 21:01.110
and failed to protect you.

21:13.970 --> 21:15.170
If I...

21:16.850 --> 21:18.610
If I didn't come back,

21:21.780 --> 21:22.870
would all this have

21:22.910 --> 21:24.100
been prevented?

21:26.070 --> 21:28.010
I've always just wanted to protect you.

21:30.550 --> 21:31.500
But I've never

21:31.500 --> 21:33.070
protected you even once.

21:34.550 --> 21:36.240
You've been hurt so much.

21:39.150 --> 21:40.580
And today...

21:42.800 --> 21:44.360
Auntie is also lying here.

21:47.260 --> 21:48.400
It's all my fault.

21:51.550 --> 21:52.710
I'm so useless.

22:00.700 --> 22:01.770
Sorry, Lu Yan.

22:11.380 --> 22:12.740
Now, I...

22:19.550 --> 22:20.950
Now I understand why you did

22:20.990 --> 22:21.790
what you did

22:21.830 --> 22:22.750
eight years ago.

22:33.600 --> 22:34.860
Jiang Chengyi.

22:43.720 --> 22:44.670
Can you...

22:48.430 --> 22:49.830
Can you hug me?

23:22.140 --> 23:22.990
Police! Freeze!

23:23.120 --> 23:23.900
Stop!

23:24.100 --> 23:24.930
Stop!

23:25.450 --> 23:26.010
Stop!

23:29.890 --> 23:30.750
Let go of me!

23:30.750 --> 23:31.510
Handcuff him!

23:31.550 --> 23:32.370
Let go!

23:38.440 --> 23:39.310
Buddy.

23:39.710 --> 23:41.430
We've met before.

23:42.350 --> 23:43.680
We're old friends then.

23:45.600 --> 23:47.400
I was just joking with her

23:48.060 --> 23:48.990
to scare her.

23:50.870 --> 23:52.240
If I'm your buddy,

23:52.780 --> 23:53.550
why'd you ask your men

23:53.550 --> 23:54.710
to beat me with bats?

23:56.250 --> 23:57.360
You locked her in the car

23:57.830 --> 23:58.390
all tied up

23:58.390 --> 23:59.590
and wanted to poison her with a gas can.

24:00.150 --> 24:01.470
You call this a joke?

24:02.320 --> 24:03.650
I admit

24:03.670 --> 24:04.390
I locked her

24:04.390 --> 24:05.720
in the car.

24:05.790 --> 24:07.190
But she kept following me.

24:07.380 --> 24:08.910
I was worried she was

24:08.930 --> 24:09.830
up to no good,

24:10.230 --> 24:11.030
or would even

24:11.050 --> 24:12.310
try to physically hurt me.

24:12.620 --> 24:13.990
That's why I did that.

24:14.010 --> 24:15.560
Strictly speaking,

24:16.550 --> 24:17.350
shouldn't this

24:17.350 --> 24:18.470
be justifiable self-defense?

24:19.000 --> 24:21.190
And the gas can you mentioned.

24:21.680 --> 24:23.370
I don't know where it came from.

24:23.580 --> 24:24.950
Is... Is there someone

24:24.990 --> 24:26.630
trying to frame me?

24:26.760 --> 24:27.430
Also,

24:27.470 --> 24:28.890
my men beat you up?

24:29.190 --> 24:30.190
Get me out of here,

24:30.220 --> 24:31.110
and I'll teach them

24:31.160 --> 24:31.870
a lesson for you.

24:32.070 --> 24:32.750
Wang Yifan.

24:33.730 --> 24:35.070
You're very familiar with this, huh?

24:36.790 --> 24:37.390
It's fine if

24:37.430 --> 24:38.470
you don't admit to this.

24:39.430 --> 24:40.750
But what you've done before

24:42.110 --> 24:42.950
is enough to warrant

24:42.990 --> 24:43.670
a life sentence.

24:48.550 --> 24:49.670
What do you mean?

24:51.630 --> 24:53.060
You murdered Yan Mei,

24:53.550 --> 24:55.880
threatened Wen Peng to hide the body

24:56.070 --> 24:57.450
and blackmailed him,

24:58.450 --> 25:00.570
and assaulted his employee, Yu Bofeng.

25:00.600 --> 25:01.390
Yu Bofeng

25:01.430 --> 25:02.400
is a superstar.

25:02.480 --> 25:03.550
How could you do that?

25:03.570 --> 25:05.240
Now, you'll have to compensate him

25:05.270 --> 25:06.350
on top of going to jail.

25:06.370 --> 25:07.170
Can you afford it?

25:08.750 --> 25:09.430
Wait,

25:09.430 --> 25:11.030
are you mistaken?

25:11.030 --> 25:12.030
I don't know any

25:12.070 --> 25:13.430
of those people. I...

25:13.630 --> 25:14.930
W-Who did I kill?

25:15.150 --> 25:17.810
I-I... blackmailed who?

25:18.280 --> 25:19.630
I'll be frank with you.

25:20.150 --> 25:20.870
We've recovered

25:20.870 --> 25:22.370
your chat history with Wen Peng.

25:23.330 --> 25:24.710
After you were arrested,

25:25.710 --> 25:26.910
Wen Peng sent another text.

25:29.740 --> 25:30.970
This is his statement.

25:31.250 --> 25:32.180
He revealed it all.

25:33.290 --> 25:34.160
I'll read it to you.

25:35.580 --> 25:36.600
Two years ago,

25:37.360 --> 25:39.060
after funeral home worker Wang Yifan

25:39.530 --> 25:40.870
started plotting after seeing Yan Mei

25:40.950 --> 25:41.670
in the hospital,

25:41.870 --> 25:43.060
he kidnapped Yan Mei

25:43.910 --> 25:44.960
and then murdered her.

25:45.150 --> 25:45.590
He...

25:45.680 --> 25:47.390
He's talking nonsense!

25:47.950 --> 25:50.070
He's... He's framing me!

25:50.160 --> 25:50.630
You...

25:50.670 --> 25:51.820
You can't believe

25:51.820 --> 25:52.950
what he said.

25:54.030 --> 25:54.710
Yan Mei's caretaker

25:54.750 --> 25:55.860
Ma Cheng said the same thing.

25:56.560 --> 25:57.790
Both Wen Peng and Ma Cheng

25:57.830 --> 25:58.630
said you did it.

25:58.670 --> 25:59.980
He must've paid off

26:00.070 --> 26:01.470
that Ma Cheng.

26:01.550 --> 26:02.830
He always uses his wealth.

26:02.830 --> 26:04.660
He... He always does this!

26:04.940 --> 26:05.880
Wang Yifan.

26:06.430 --> 26:07.110
This is a

26:07.150 --> 26:08.310
legal procedure.

26:08.350 --> 26:09.490
It's about evidence.

26:09.670 --> 26:10.390
Now all the evidence

26:10.430 --> 26:11.180
points at you.

26:11.240 --> 26:12.310
You killed Yan Mei

26:12.390 --> 26:13.320
two years ago!

26:13.510 --> 26:15.930
He came to me two years ago!

26:25.310 --> 26:26.470
About two years ago,

26:27.120 --> 26:28.570
he came to the funeral home

26:28.880 --> 26:29.910
and asked me to get rid of

26:29.910 --> 26:30.590
a body for him

26:31.350 --> 26:32.910
without documenting it.

26:33.470 --> 26:34.550
As you know,

26:34.990 --> 26:35.990
I'm just an employee

26:35.990 --> 26:36.750
at a funeral home.

26:36.870 --> 26:38.190
How'd I dare to do that?

26:39.190 --> 26:39.820
Besides,

26:39.840 --> 26:41.030
all the procedures

26:41.370 --> 26:42.450
in the funeral home

26:42.510 --> 26:44.110
must be carefully reviewed.

26:44.370 --> 26:46.030
It's super strict.

26:46.790 --> 26:47.310
But...

26:47.870 --> 26:49.100
But later he said

26:49.990 --> 26:51.150
he'd pay me

26:51.190 --> 26:52.360
300,000 yuan.

26:52.390 --> 26:53.770
I... I...

26:53.950 --> 26:55.150
I couldn't resist.

26:56.410 --> 26:57.970
Who did he ask you to cremate?

26:58.450 --> 26:59.800
I don't know.

27:00.220 --> 27:00.870
Maybe...

27:00.950 --> 27:02.590
it might be that person

27:02.590 --> 27:03.760
you just mentioned.

27:04.350 --> 27:05.810
I just know it's an old lady.

27:06.320 --> 27:07.820
She was so skinny.

27:07.840 --> 27:09.070
She obviously died of illness.

27:09.810 --> 27:10.880
How old was she?

27:10.900 --> 27:12.440
About 60 years old, I think.

27:13.580 --> 27:15.460
But I didn't look at her carefully.

27:15.490 --> 27:16.930
I don't dare to speculate.

27:17.430 --> 27:19.350
After the old lady was sent to me,

27:20.420 --> 27:22.230
it felt like she's been dead for a long time.

27:22.590 --> 27:23.390
Her body already

27:23.390 --> 27:24.590
started decomposing.

27:25.900 --> 27:26.660
And then?

27:27.140 --> 27:28.680
Getting rid of the body and info

27:28.750 --> 27:30.190
in a funeral home

27:30.430 --> 27:32.020
is basically impossible.

27:32.930 --> 27:34.120
So I...

27:34.230 --> 27:35.500
I secretly

27:35.920 --> 27:37.910
transported the body away

27:38.230 --> 27:38.910
and buried it.

27:40.110 --> 27:41.030
Where?

27:41.520 --> 27:42.730
On the North Mountain of Chengzhou,

27:42.950 --> 27:44.910
at the pavilion of the ecological park.

27:47.610 --> 27:48.580
Officer.

27:48.830 --> 27:51.230
I've told you everything.

27:51.470 --> 27:53.960
Will it help with today's matter?

27:55.400 --> 27:56.390
It depends on your performance.

27:59.870 --> 28:02.590
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

28:11.840 --> 28:12.470
Here.

28:13.180 --> 28:13.910
Here.

28:14.390 --> 28:15.440
What happened?

28:15.460 --> 28:16.670
How did the car accident happen?

28:18.730 --> 28:20.600
A truck crashed into her

28:21.570 --> 28:23.430
when she was crossing the road.

28:23.770 --> 28:25.660
She's still in the critical stage.

28:29.740 --> 28:31.390
Did you find the driver?

28:32.150 --> 28:33.060
Yes.

28:33.920 --> 28:35.840
There were no traces of braking at the scene.

28:36.390 --> 28:37.810
I suspect it was intentional.

28:38.630 --> 28:39.470
Intentional?

28:41.150 --> 28:42.820
Could it be Wen Peng?

28:43.290 --> 28:44.690
We don’t know yet.

28:46.680 --> 28:47.610
Captain Jiang.

28:48.590 --> 28:49.630
Keep watch.

28:54.950 --> 28:55.710
How is it?

28:55.730 --> 28:56.590
Last night,

28:56.630 --> 28:57.450
Qin Yue caught Wu Di.

28:57.470 --> 28:58.380
We're interrogating him.

28:59.230 --> 29:00.750
Based on the current evidence,

29:00.770 --> 29:01.750
this hit-and-run driver

29:01.780 --> 29:02.860
and the last truck driver

29:02.890 --> 29:03.560
are linked.

29:03.690 --> 29:05.270
It's Wen Peng's assistant, Wu Di.

29:06.360 --> 29:07.350
We've also heard back

29:07.350 --> 29:08.230
from Cyber Investigation.

29:08.480 --> 29:09.740
He spread the rumors about you

29:09.790 --> 29:10.650
and Professor Yu too.

29:13.590 --> 29:14.840
And Wang Yifan?

29:15.020 --> 29:15.980
He admitted that

29:16.320 --> 29:17.960
Wen Peng instigated him.

29:20.460 --> 29:21.610
Request for a warrant now

29:21.990 --> 29:23.000
to arrest Wen Peng.

29:23.190 --> 29:23.920
Yes.

29:32.720 --> 29:33.800
Police.

29:33.910 --> 29:35.150
Mr. Wen's not in the office.

29:35.150 --> 29:35.830
Hello. Excuse me.

29:35.830 --> 29:36.150
I saw him

29:36.150 --> 29:37.340
come in this morning.

29:37.990 --> 29:38.510
He hasn't been back

29:38.510 --> 29:39.190
since he left

29:39.190 --> 29:39.870
yesterday afternoon.

29:39.870 --> 29:41.190
We really don't know his schedule.

29:41.210 --> 29:42.910
I'm asking you where he is now!

29:42.940 --> 29:44.300
He's not in the office.

29:44.910 --> 29:45.480
Search.

29:45.600 --> 29:46.460
-Yes.
-Yes.

29:47.240 --> 29:48.710
Leave first.

29:52.070 --> 29:52.730
Jiang.

30:04.270 --> 30:05.590
I told you that

30:05.620 --> 30:06.790
as long as you and Lu Yan

30:06.810 --> 30:07.990
are together,

30:08.640 --> 30:09.410
maybe

30:09.680 --> 30:11.240
even more people will suffer.

30:11.550 --> 30:13.340
This time, it's Lu Yan's mother.

30:13.990 --> 30:14.980
Guess who

30:15.280 --> 30:16.650
the next one will be.

30:29.880 --> 30:30.870
Liu Hao.

30:31.340 --> 30:32.400
Secret room on the 2nd floor.

30:53.250 --> 30:55.160
Ask the trace inspectors to come here.

30:55.280 --> 30:55.800
Yes.

30:57.090 --> 31:00.260
[Lu Yan, will you go to Lake Baikal with me in the future?]

31:02.220 --> 31:02.720
Director.

31:02.740 --> 31:04.020
We retrieved all surveillance footage

31:04.070 --> 31:05.350
along his company's building.

31:06.320 --> 31:07.010
Wen Peng

31:07.050 --> 31:08.770
first disguised as a cleaner

31:08.790 --> 31:10.010
to evade our stakeout

31:10.030 --> 31:11.050
and walked away.

31:11.230 --> 31:13.920
He then boarded bus no. 39

31:13.950 --> 31:15.860
and got off at the suburb station.

31:16.210 --> 31:17.340
Then he disappeared.

31:17.550 --> 31:18.540
We've also checked

31:18.570 --> 31:19.610
all his properties

31:19.640 --> 31:20.580
in Ninghai.

31:20.610 --> 31:21.750
There's only one villa.

31:21.810 --> 31:22.710
This was what we found

31:22.710 --> 31:23.760
at Wen Peng's house.

31:28.360 --> 31:30.270
From yesterday afternoon till now,

31:30.330 --> 31:31.350
Wen Peng's phone

31:31.390 --> 31:32.780
has been switched off.

31:32.810 --> 31:35.870
There's no record of credit card use, cash withdrawal,

31:35.890 --> 31:37.690
or hotel expenses either.

31:37.870 --> 31:38.950
A grown man like him

31:38.990 --> 31:40.080
just disappeared?

31:45.350 --> 31:46.100
Jiang.

31:46.690 --> 31:47.740
Tell me what you think.

31:49.240 --> 31:49.930
Director Xing.

31:50.190 --> 31:51.390
I think based on Wen Peng's

31:51.390 --> 31:52.190
usual approach,

31:53.360 --> 31:54.630
he should still be in Ninghai.

31:54.970 --> 31:55.830
And he must be

31:55.870 --> 31:58.140
waiting for the next chance to attack again.

32:00.590 --> 32:01.180
Listen.

32:02.500 --> 32:04.690
The suspect Wen Peng

32:04.880 --> 32:06.630
is suspected of many serious crimes.

32:06.670 --> 32:07.780
From now on,

32:08.050 --> 32:09.460
it's a citywide search.

32:10.140 --> 32:11.420
All departments must be vigilant

32:11.470 --> 32:12.110
and cooperate

32:12.150 --> 32:13.300
fully and closely.

32:13.620 --> 32:14.920
Don't let Wen Peng

32:14.980 --> 32:16.190
escape from Ninghai

32:16.210 --> 32:17.240
and get away scot free!

32:17.450 --> 32:18.110
-Yes!
-Yes!

32:18.830 --> 32:21.490
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

32:32.550 --> 32:33.540
Jiang.

32:34.150 --> 32:34.710
Zhong.

32:37.030 --> 32:37.750
How's Auntie?

32:38.150 --> 32:39.110
The doctor just came

32:39.150 --> 32:40.230
and talked about brain swelling.

32:40.250 --> 32:41.290
We need to wait and see.

32:41.930 --> 32:42.550
And Lu Yan?

32:42.580 --> 32:43.360
How is she?

32:44.670 --> 32:45.670
She's the same,

32:45.690 --> 32:46.690
not eating or drinking.

32:46.710 --> 32:47.830
Just standing there.

32:49.080 --> 32:50.330
Thanks for your help.

32:51.070 --> 32:51.910
Don't say that.

32:51.910 --> 32:52.960
We're buddies.

32:53.220 --> 32:54.280
You too.

32:54.290 --> 32:55.270
Why couldn't you

32:55.310 --> 32:55.950
just call Lu Yan?

32:55.980 --> 32:57.360
Must I be your messenger?

32:58.950 --> 33:00.470
If there's anything,

33:01.190 --> 33:02.470
call me anytime.

33:02.710 --> 33:03.350
Okay.

33:04.710 --> 33:05.470
Jiang Chengyi?

33:06.430 --> 33:07.360
Why did he call you

33:07.400 --> 33:08.190
instead of Lu Yan?

33:09.050 --> 33:10.900
I understand Jiang.

33:10.930 --> 33:12.000
He can't face Lu Yan

33:12.200 --> 33:13.600
until Wen Peng's arrested.

33:14.480 --> 33:15.810
You men are really...

33:15.870 --> 33:17.240
It's not that complex.

33:17.390 --> 33:18.450
Tell him now

33:18.470 --> 33:19.530
to come over after work.

33:20.070 --> 33:20.950
Got it.

33:27.430 --> 33:27.950
Captain Jiang.

33:28.800 --> 33:29.550
Li Ruonan's mother's

33:29.550 --> 33:30.470
DNA test report is out.

33:41.510 --> 33:42.170
Okay.

33:45.420 --> 33:47.040
Go to the detention center to interrogate Li Ruonan.

33:47.230 --> 33:50.070
[Police]

33:50.810 --> 33:52.630
During the investigation,

33:53.510 --> 33:55.720
we've also been looking for your mother.

33:56.230 --> 33:57.270
We found

33:57.990 --> 34:00.460
a relatively fresher corpse

34:01.670 --> 34:02.960
on a barren mountain

34:03.310 --> 34:04.650
in your hometown Chengzhou

34:05.570 --> 34:06.470
and compared it

34:06.510 --> 34:07.150
with your DNA.

34:08.960 --> 34:09.830
I can tell you that

34:10.620 --> 34:11.670
it should be your mother.

34:13.929 --> 34:16.980
[Forensic Expert Opinion]

34:20.350 --> 34:22.170
Are you trying to trick me with this again?

34:23.489 --> 34:24.270
It's useless.

34:24.710 --> 34:25.820
I wouldn't lie to you.

34:26.310 --> 34:27.199
There's no need.

34:29.790 --> 34:30.920
These photos

34:31.250 --> 34:32.429
were found

34:32.429 --> 34:33.790
in Wen Peng's computer.

34:34.239 --> 34:35.170
Some were photos

34:35.350 --> 34:36.989
of your mother when she was alive.

34:38.010 --> 34:39.520
But most of them

34:39.929 --> 34:41.280
were fabricated

34:41.340 --> 34:43.000
by Wen Peng.

35:07.500 --> 35:08.500
No way.

35:09.980 --> 35:11.870
These lies won't work on me.

35:12.330 --> 35:13.560
I just said

35:14.120 --> 35:15.930
I have no reason to lie to you.

35:16.540 --> 35:17.680
Also, at this point,

35:18.590 --> 35:19.510
I wouldn't deceive you

35:19.510 --> 35:20.470
with such a thing.

35:21.600 --> 35:23.150
Wen Peng has been

35:23.800 --> 35:25.610
using these photos of your mother...

35:27.190 --> 35:28.130
to manipulate you

35:28.650 --> 35:29.940
to do all sorts of things for him.

35:31.420 --> 35:32.600
But actually,

35:33.610 --> 35:34.700
two years ago,

35:35.380 --> 35:36.880
your mom'd already died of illness.

35:36.910 --> 35:37.810
Nonsense!

35:40.630 --> 35:41.710
After Wen Peng

35:41.710 --> 35:42.900
found out,

35:43.200 --> 35:44.480
instead of telling you

35:44.750 --> 35:45.510
so you could

35:45.550 --> 35:46.790
see your mother for the last time,

35:46.810 --> 35:48.840
he chose to hide

35:48.870 --> 35:50.390
your mother's death.

35:51.580 --> 35:52.590
In the end, your mother

35:52.630 --> 35:54.050
didn't die peacefully

35:54.340 --> 35:56.320
and was buried on a barren mountain by Wen Peng.

35:56.580 --> 35:57.510
You always thought

35:57.510 --> 35:59.030
he was taking care of your mother for you.

35:59.070 --> 36:00.430
But in fact,

36:00.550 --> 36:02.100
you were helping him

36:02.750 --> 36:03.870
do all sorts of things.

36:04.800 --> 36:05.890
He has been

36:06.110 --> 36:07.910
using you through your mother.

36:08.420 --> 36:09.510
This is all evidence

36:09.540 --> 36:11.760
we uncovered bit by bit.

36:13.190 --> 36:15.110
Everything is true.

36:18.330 --> 36:19.260
Li Ruonan.

36:20.210 --> 36:21.370
This time...

36:23.560 --> 36:24.990
should be my last time

36:25.030 --> 36:25.750
interrogating you.

36:26.690 --> 36:28.140
Your confession

36:29.030 --> 36:30.680
doesn't matter to us anymore.

36:31.640 --> 36:33.260
We have the evidence

36:33.830 --> 36:36.320
that Wen Peng hired you as a killer.

36:36.500 --> 36:37.440
I'm here today

36:37.920 --> 36:40.390
to tell you everything

36:42.040 --> 36:43.560
so that you can be prepared.

36:47.390 --> 36:48.030
That's it.

36:49.410 --> 36:50.290
Take her back.

36:51.950 --> 36:52.820
Don't touch me.

36:57.890 --> 36:58.660
I'll talk.

37:06.160 --> 37:07.600
About two years ago,

37:09.510 --> 37:11.030
my mom's illness was getting worse.

37:12.140 --> 37:13.540
I couldn't afford the medical fees.

37:16.510 --> 37:17.590
So I went to his film crew

37:17.630 --> 37:18.660
as a stunt double.

37:19.670 --> 37:21.070
Every penny counts,

37:21.090 --> 37:21.760
I thought.

37:36.560 --> 37:37.570
You're quite a fighter.

37:39.250 --> 37:40.580
You want me to pay?

37:40.600 --> 37:41.380
I'm broke.

37:41.670 --> 37:43.140
They deducted my pay.

37:43.170 --> 37:44.230
They deserved it.

37:45.760 --> 37:46.930
Are you short of money?

37:51.910 --> 37:53.070
500 a day for a stunt double

37:53.090 --> 37:54.160
is quite low indeed.

37:54.530 --> 37:56.790
Why don't you work for me?

37:57.150 --> 37:57.830
Name your price.

37:59.280 --> 38:00.390
What do you need me to do?

38:02.180 --> 38:03.570
I haven't decided yet.

38:03.670 --> 38:05.190
I'll tell you after I've made up my mind.

38:07.230 --> 38:08.590
But can you tell me

38:08.610 --> 38:10.010
why you're so short of money?

38:10.860 --> 38:12.080
My mother's sick.

38:12.910 --> 38:14.500
I need money for her treatment.

38:17.000 --> 38:18.260
Then how about this?

38:18.800 --> 38:20.530
Just work for me from now on.

38:21.070 --> 38:22.610
I'll cover your mother's

38:22.830 --> 38:23.760
medical expenses.

38:25.760 --> 38:26.660
Everything?

38:27.550 --> 38:29.090
Do you know how much I need?

38:36.310 --> 38:37.510
Give me your account number.

38:47.290 --> 38:47.780
[Transfer]

38:47.830 --> 38:49.960
[Transfer 300,000 yuan]

38:56.380 --> 38:58.820
[Your account ending with 9172 has received 300,000 yuan from the account ending with 3393]

39:01.190 --> 39:02.660
If you don't agree,

39:02.700 --> 39:04.220
take this 300,000 as a gift.

39:04.270 --> 39:05.520
If you agree,

39:06.680 --> 39:08.050
contact me with this phone.

39:14.350 --> 39:15.780
But there's a price.

39:16.660 --> 39:18.350
All your identification info

39:18.350 --> 39:19.310
is under my control.

39:20.350 --> 39:21.570
You can't question

39:21.990 --> 39:23.350
what I ask you to do.

39:24.690 --> 39:25.300
Okay?

39:27.310 --> 39:27.950
I agree.

39:31.470 --> 39:32.260
Later,

39:33.030 --> 39:33.910
he sent my mom

39:33.910 --> 39:35.650
to the best hospital

39:36.230 --> 39:38.020
with the best medicine

39:38.510 --> 39:40.150
and hired a caretaker for her.

39:42.670 --> 39:44.530
So I started to work for him.

39:45.070 --> 39:46.900
What exactly did you do?

39:48.030 --> 39:48.750
At first,

39:49.870 --> 39:51.060
I just threatened

39:51.110 --> 39:52.230
his competitors

39:53.700 --> 39:55.090
and stalked some people.

39:56.640 --> 39:57.330
Later,

39:58.470 --> 39:59.790
he asked me to disguise as Deng Man.

40:02.420 --> 40:03.290
After that,

40:04.020 --> 40:04.950
it was murder.

40:38.680 --> 40:39.480
Remember,

40:39.510 --> 40:40.960
just let her see it.

40:41.140 --> 40:42.320
Don't hurt her.

40:43.140 --> 40:44.050
Got it.

40:56.920 --> 40:59.240
Do it as planned tonight.

40:59.530 --> 41:00.220
Remember,

41:00.540 --> 41:01.830
you must throw Wang Qianqian

41:01.850 --> 41:03.080
into the artificial lake.

41:23.710 --> 41:25.240
Why is it you?

41:25.670 --> 41:27.540
You're the boss she was talking about?

41:27.900 --> 41:28.800
Are you crazy?

41:28.820 --> 41:30.020
Why did you kidnap me?

41:34.690 --> 41:36.090
Over the phone that day,

41:36.670 --> 41:37.870
I couldn't hear clearly.

41:39.070 --> 41:39.880
So,

41:39.980 --> 41:42.270
I personally came to ask you.

41:43.840 --> 41:45.260
Did you warn me about

41:45.660 --> 41:46.780
my involvement with

41:48.090 --> 41:48.960
Deng Man's death?

41:52.990 --> 41:55.570
I just said it out of spite.

41:56.600 --> 41:57.860
You just happened

41:57.920 --> 41:59.300
to call me

41:59.330 --> 42:00.820
when I was fuming.

42:00.880 --> 42:03.090
But I wasn't targeting you.

42:03.530 --> 42:04.990
We've known each other for years.

42:05.070 --> 42:06.230
Do you have to kidnap me

42:06.230 --> 42:07.770
here for this?

42:12.220 --> 42:12.910
Did you

42:12.950 --> 42:14.320
not understand what I just said?

42:14.730 --> 42:15.930
I'll say it again.

42:18.390 --> 42:19.310
Did you tell me

42:19.310 --> 42:20.670
on the phone that...

42:22.380 --> 42:23.630
I'm also part of

42:25.110 --> 42:25.870
Deng Man's death?

42:28.710 --> 42:30.280
If anything happens to me,

42:31.830 --> 42:32.710
no one can live.

42:33.440 --> 42:34.630
I did say that.

42:36.070 --> 42:37.070
But that's because

42:37.110 --> 42:38.530
you forced me into it.

42:38.750 --> 42:40.670
You blamed me as soon as you called.

42:41.350 --> 42:43.240
Besides, you were the one

42:43.630 --> 42:45.400
who came up with that idea.

42:45.950 --> 42:46.630
So...

42:48.470 --> 42:49.750
you have evidence?

42:57.190 --> 42:58.230
Before cooperating,

42:58.270 --> 42:59.190
I told you that

43:00.390 --> 43:01.830
we'll each take what we need.

43:03.110 --> 43:04.060
It was this way in the past,

43:04.540 --> 43:05.880
and it still is now.

43:07.530 --> 43:08.450
But this time,

43:10.670 --> 43:11.470
you've crossed the line.

43:20.150 --> 43:21.170
I've been trying

43:21.230 --> 43:22.590
to find a chance to explain

43:22.590 --> 43:24.270
this to you.

43:24.430 --> 43:26.030
I was wrong for this.

43:26.050 --> 43:27.470
I know you love Lu Yan.

43:27.550 --> 43:28.630
I pushed her down.

43:28.660 --> 43:30.280
I went too far.

43:30.710 --> 43:32.380
But from my point of view,

43:32.430 --> 43:33.240
think about it.

43:33.270 --> 43:35.510
She really went too far.

43:35.670 --> 43:36.430
All these years,

43:36.430 --> 43:37.390
I've never touched

43:37.410 --> 43:38.990
even a hair of hers.

43:39.020 --> 43:40.350
But what'd she do?

43:40.390 --> 43:41.430
She gathered so many people

43:41.470 --> 43:43.730
to mess with me at my big event.

43:44.370 --> 43:46.330
Now my career and life are gone.

43:46.390 --> 43:47.510
I-If it were you,

43:47.530 --> 43:48.610
wouldn't you be furious too?

43:48.650 --> 43:50.210
You wouldn't have just let it go.

43:57.170 --> 43:58.390
So why'd you kidnap me?

43:58.430 --> 43:59.570
What do you want me to do?

43:59.790 --> 44:00.510
Tell me.

44:06.500 --> 44:07.760
Give me the evidence.

44:08.400 --> 44:10.290
I'll find a way to send you abroad.

44:11.780 --> 44:13.380
I can give you the evidence.

44:14.290 --> 44:16.110
But you have to send me abroad first.

44:16.390 --> 44:17.100
Ding Jing.

44:18.200 --> 44:20.770
Do you know what

44:21.120 --> 44:22.750
I hate the most?

44:27.280 --> 44:28.680
Disobedience.

44:31.750 --> 44:32.230
People...

44:34.830 --> 44:35.390
who...

44:37.500 --> 44:38.490
disobey!

44:41.640 --> 44:42.760
I'll behave.

44:48.790 --> 44:49.550
What do you mean?

44:50.300 --> 44:51.110
I've searched

44:51.150 --> 44:52.440
Ding Jing's home and company.

44:52.990 --> 44:54.640
I didn't find anything.

44:55.250 --> 44:55.880
Could it be that

44:55.880 --> 44:56.950
she doesn't have evidence?

44:57.350 --> 44:58.300
Can you guarantee that?

45:00.130 --> 45:01.040
I'm sorry.

45:02.250 --> 45:03.770
If you still want to see her,

45:04.470 --> 45:05.710
you know what to do.

45:06.070 --> 45:07.180
Don't worry.

45:08.730 --> 45:09.920
I will find it.

45:13.190 --> 45:15.000
I really had no choice.

45:16.940 --> 45:18.710
There's no other way I could

45:18.790 --> 45:20.750
get enough money for her kidney transplant.

45:22.020 --> 45:23.220
I didn't expect

45:25.200 --> 45:26.930
him to break his promise.

45:29.890 --> 45:30.760
Do you have

45:30.790 --> 45:32.630
any records of your liaison

45:32.960 --> 45:34.000
with him?

45:36.170 --> 45:37.810
Apart from transferring money to me

45:39.120 --> 45:40.070
with his phone

45:40.070 --> 45:41.230
when we first met,

45:42.380 --> 45:43.320
he always

45:44.330 --> 45:45.940
called me.

45:47.270 --> 45:48.760
He gave me a phone.

45:49.980 --> 45:51.560
When you caught me,

45:51.580 --> 45:53.150
I destroyed it.

45:58.110 --> 45:59.290
When you later

45:59.560 --> 46:00.870
went to Ding Jing's home,

46:01.640 --> 46:02.660
what were you looking for?

46:03.010 --> 46:04.340
Ding Jing said...

46:07.410 --> 46:08.890
she had evidence

46:10.080 --> 46:11.450
of Wen Peng

46:12.430 --> 46:14.230
killing Deng Man with her.

46:16.390 --> 46:17.890
I think it's a USB.

46:31.170 --> 46:32.200
Li Ruonan.

46:34.520 --> 46:35.630
I don't think

46:36.060 --> 46:36.830
we'd ever

46:36.830 --> 46:38.230
meet again.

46:41.470 --> 46:42.410
Tell me.

46:43.110 --> 46:45.810
Is there anything you want

46:46.120 --> 46:48.240
to say or do?

46:48.750 --> 46:49.550
Tell me.

46:50.870 --> 46:52.160
If I can make it happen,

46:52.830 --> 46:53.590
I'll help you.

46:54.670 --> 46:55.390
Thank you.

47:03.510 --> 47:04.230
If...

47:04.560 --> 47:05.470
If...

47:07.880 --> 47:09.230
If it's possible...

47:12.430 --> 47:14.600
I think when I die,

47:16.660 --> 47:19.080
I'd like to be buried with my mom.

47:24.850 --> 47:25.490
Okay?
